Wednesday, May 1, 1996

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

96-113. Thompson v. Utomo.

Lucas County, No. L-95-034. This cause is pending before the court on the certification of conflict by the Court of Appeals for Lucas County. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

*1469ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
